The '''Yresilini''' were a [[Species/Legends|species]] found in the [[Unknown Regions/Legends|Unknown Regions]] of [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]]. The species had at least one [[Gender/Legends|gender]], which was masculine, had the capacity to laugh, and were regarded as untrainable creatures by the [[Chiss/Legends|Chiss]] species.<ref name="CC">''[[Star Wars: Galactic Battlegrounds: Clone Campaigns]]''</ref>

Prior to the [[First Battle of Geonosis/Legends|outbreak]] of the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]] in [[22 BBY/Legends|22 BBY]],<ref name="Explain">According to ''[[Star Wars: Galactic Battlegrounds: Clone Campaigns]]'', [[Sev'rance Tann/Legends|Sev'rance Tann]] had left the [[Unknown Regions/Legends|Unknown Regions]] prior to her involvement in the [[First Battle of Geonosis/Legends|First Battle of Geonosis]], which occurred in [[22 BBY/Legends|22 BBY]] according to ''[[The New Essential Chronology]]''.</ref> a [[Unidentified professor (Chiss Academy)|professor]] at the [[Chiss Academy]] challenged a young student named [[Sev'rance Tann/Legends|Sev'rance Tann]] to train a group of Yresilini into an [[Army/Legends|army]]. Tann began her assignment by selecting an [[Unidentified first Yresilini general|individual]] Yresilini as a [[General/Legends|general]] and attempted to teach him a series of commands. The general responded by laughing at Tann, prompting his fellow Yresilini to laugh as well. Tann had the general [[Death/Legends|executed]] in front of his [[Trooper/Legends|troops]], and selected a [[Unidentified second Yresilini general|successor]], who led the Yresilini to follow her orders completely. Tann received high marks from her [[Professor/Legends|professor]] and continued on a military career, with the story of her taming the Yresilini being retold amongst [[Soldier/Legends|soldiers]] under her command.<ref name="CC" />

==Behind the scenes==
The Yresilini were first mentioned in Sev'rance Tann's databank entry for the [[2002]] [[LucasArts]] [[Star Wars video games|video game]] [[Star Wars: Galactic Battlegrounds: Clone Campaigns|''Clone Campaigns'']], an expansion of the [[2001]] game ''[[Star Wars: Galactic Battlegrounds]]''.<ref name="CC" />

